## Installation

This repo was tested on Python 3.5+ and PyTorch 0.4.1/1.0.0
Please refer to pyroch website for installiation based on your system 

### With pip

PyTorch pretrained bert can be installed by pip as follows:
```bash
pip install pytorch-pretrained-bert
```

## folder structure 

- ./libs 		-- contrain all modules you need to use 
- ./config.py  		-- most parameters you need to use 
- ./example.py 		-- a working example on SST2
